# Funnel Skill Standards

- Store project skills in `.cursor/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`.
- Skill name must be lowercase with hyphen separators.
- `SKILL.md` frontmatter must include:
  - `name`
  - `description`
- Description must include:
  - WHAT the skill does.
  - WHEN to use it (trigger terms).
- Optional support files allowed: `reference.md`, `examples.md`, `scripts/`.
